item.title: CVE-2023-1110|2023-08-16T11:03:26.120Z -- unknown -- yellow%20yard%20searchbar
item.description: The Yellow Yard Searchbar WordPress plugin before 2.8.12 does not validate and escape some of its shortcode attributes before outputting them back in a page/post where the shortcode is embed, which could allow users with the contributor role and above to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks
